{"type": "article", "id": 26034, "title": "口袋式支架", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-27T07:19:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115051QnGu7NFIxScvr5zt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个名为 Percha 的口袋式支架很好地诠释了“有限的资源是如何通过优秀的创意得以解决生活上的问题”。支架的设计非常简单，可以很轻松地挂在挂钩或者门把上，无论是居家还是办公的场合都具有很高的实用性。每一个支架都由手工制作，售价为 57.77 美元，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/287837351/wall-hung-portable-magazine-rack-modern\">链接</a>进行购买，如果需要个性化上色等服务需要额外收取费用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115050iLHSN2RJvTOBcVbg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021150506jgBCIPoXJVxcAmd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115051szkM1RnYmrg0XuAN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}